.TH "ipr_reset_freeze" 9 "ipr_reset_freeze" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ipr_reset_freeze \- Hold off all I/O activity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ipr_reset_freeze
.BI "(struct ipr_cmnd *ipr_cmd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ipr_cmd" 12
ipr command struct
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
If the PCI slot is frozen, hold off all I/O
activity; then, as soon as the slot is available again,
initiate an adapter reset.
